TAX_GROUP: Fishes - Freshwater and Anadromous Bony, Cartilaginous; Lampreys
COSEWIC_SUMMARY: The species was considered a single unit and designated Not at Risk in April 1989. When the species was split into three separate units in April 2016, the Great Lakes - Upper St. Lawrence populations was designated Endangered and the other two designated Not at Risk.
